{
  "stem": "3952.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sure enough, many of our friends went, and they were not well trained.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All we knew was [INAUDIBLE], how to dismantle, and the-- and the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we didn't even know how to put on our [INAUDIBLE], you know, that army rucksack and the bullets and everything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know how to put that on, because that we never had in Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got to Israel-- after 20 months and one day in Cyprus, we closed the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I took the ping pong table with us, and we came to Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we took it to the camp, straight to the army camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I settle-- I set up a ping pong tournament there in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and one-- one guy from Czechoslovakia was the first, and I was the second, and my brother was the third.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we all got four days' leave because we won a surprise for winning the tournament.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were many people playing ping pong, but we were the best.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we got the prize of four days' leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when we come back, all our friends were gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They became the personal bodyguards for the president in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had a fantastic job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were doing their six or seven hours of watching around the premises of Dr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Weizman ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the rest, during the day, they would work, they would build, they would make some money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, where are we going?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and now they split us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a law that two brothers cannot be in the same unit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they sent my brother to one place, and me they sent to another place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What are you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I've always been with my brother since I'm liberated.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
